Orlando Pirates players dejected during the 2022 Nedbank Cup quarter final match between Marumo Gallants and Orlando Pirates. BackpagePix/Samuel Shivambu JOHANNESBURG - Orlando Pirates' season isn't getting any better. Straight after suffering a defeat in the Soweto Derby, the Buccaneers have now been bumped out of the Nedbank Cup by Marumo Gallants. The sides were tied at 1-all after extra-time and Gallants proved too sharp for Pirates in the penalty shootout. It ended 5-4 with Gallants though to the quarter-finals.